description.standard: A mix of laidback hip-hop, R&B, and the occasional chilled-out electronic soul track, this playlist is calibrated to carry you into low lights and late nights. Because “after hours” doesn't mean it's over. We regularly refresh this set with new music. If you like a song, add it to your library.
description.short: Hip-hop and R&B for low lights and late nights.
